Class ApiModels

java.lang.Object
gabrielLopes.project2425.DevPackage.QuickFixApp.ServerInterfacePackage.ApiModels
public class ApiModels extends Object
Contains all data models used for communicating with the backend. Each class represents a request or response body exchanged through the API.
